          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The yields of 30 nuclear protons from Ni-60,61,62",
                "targets were measured by the induced-activity method.",
                "Comparison of the experimental values with calculations",
                "carried out by RUDSTAM modified formula confirms the",
                "exponential dependence of the yields upon the",
                "difference between the isospins of the target and",
                "recoil nuclei. The parameters of the RUDSTAM correction",
                "term were obtained by a fitting procedure. The",
                "dependence of the isomer relations on the number of",
                "nucleons is discussed."
              ]
            }
          ],
